    footer.footer
      .verybottom
        .container
          .row
            center
              em
                | HBCUHacks is a program of 
                a href="http://www.blackfounders.com" target="blank"
                  | Black Founders
                | . Our mission is to increase the number of black entrepreneurs in tech.
